=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Guides_Tour_of_UGens_ex14 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright noisy sound, with noise oscillator character around 457 Hz, featuring punchy attack and percussive envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, energy distribution is early, filtered with highpass character, and spectrally rich.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: percussive
  envelope_flatness: sustained
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: noisy
  spectral_complexity_mean: rich
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: highpass
  temporal_centroid: early

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 456.8329
  harmonic_decay_rate: 0.6801
  harmonic_regularity: 0.0206
  pitch_clarity: 2.5528
  inharmonicity: 0.9229
  type: noise
[filter]
  spectral_slope: 6.6392
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Tour of UGens Example 14
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Guides/Tour_of_UGens.html
// Tags: Tour_of_UGens, Guides
// ---
// --- Example 14 ---
{ Blip.ar(XLine.kr(20000,200,6),100,0.2) }.play;
{ Blip.ar(XLine.kr(100,15000,6),100,0.2) }.play; // no aliasing
// modulate number of harmonics
{ Blip.ar(200,Line.kr(1,100,20),0.2) }.play;
